Package: estCost
Type: Package
Title: Estimation and Calculation of Costs and Financial Metrics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kelompok 10
Maintainer: Kelompok 10 <shranindya12@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive tool for estimating and calculating various financial metrics including:
    - Travel costs
    - Production costs
    - Selling prices
    - Loan installments
    - Profit and loss
    - Discounts
    - Profit-sharing among parties
    - Taxes
    - Total shopping expenses
    - Break-Even Point (BEP) analysis.
    This package simplifies financial decision-making for individuals and businesses by providing easy-to-use functions.
